OOC: Not much happened here, we had maybe two stories where we went out into
the city.  So now we&#39;re getting more use out of it. :P

BIC:

Coming to almost a complete stop, the ship slowly descended and locked into
an automatic sequence. As soon as they touched down, the doors on the roof
shut and some maintenance equipment immediately started working over the
ship.  Having been out for so long without proper maintenance, it was going
to be a while before it could fly again.

Creep was regaining consciousness, but still was a bit stunned.  Celeron
picked her up and carried her off the ship, hoping not to suddenly be
attacked.

&quot;Celeron to Kratos.  I&#39;ve returned to the base.  What&#39;s going on outside?
Did we have some sort of recruiting drive?  There are predecons everywhere.&quot;

Then pushing a button next to the door.  &quot;Security override @#$@#$@#333312@#@
Celeron.&quot;

&quot;Override accepted.&quot; responded a computerized voice. &quot;Access-way clear.&quot;


OOC: Creep is Robert&#39;s character, I don&#39;t know what he intended with her, so
I&#39;m just bringing her back to the base and he can pick her up if and when he
comes back.

